title: fix your rank queue system please

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
i have gold v, sliver 2, plat5, plat 5 in the team, im plat 4.
they have plat 3, gold 1, gold 1, gold 2, gold 1.

how sliver 2 and gold 5 in our game, both of them just cant do anything in lane/jungle.

just lost the game i guess?

replies.body:
There will always be someone on a team who's the highest division and someone on the team who's the lowest division.

There's a one in five chance it'll be you.
